  "texts": [
    "For example, a document about genetics is more likely to be also about disease than x-ray astronomy (Blei and Lafferty 2006a).",
    "This leads to better Page 17 of 30 18 expressiveness than LDA.",
    "Liu et al (2019) follow the VAE-based NTM and use centralized transformation flow to capture topic correlations.",
    "To effectively infer the transformation flow, they present the transformation flow lower bound to regulate the KL divergence term.",
    "Lifelong NTMs are proposed to solve the challenge of data sparsity, similar to short text NTMs but in a continual lifelong learning fashion."
